---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Mounjaro for Weight Loss"
  description="Learn about Mounjaro (tirzepatide) for weight loss - how it works, effectiveness, side effects, and eligibility at Logan Health."
  canonical="https://loganhealth.co.uk/mounjaro"
  keywords="Mounjaro, tirzepatide, GLP-1, weight loss, Logan Health, South East London"
  ogTitle="Mounjaro for Weight Loss | Logan Health"
  ogDescription="Learn about Mounjaro (tirzepatide) for weight loss - how it works, effectiveness, side effects, and eligibility at Logan Health."
  ogType="article"
>
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="section" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary-dark) 0%, var(--color-primary) 100%); color: var(--color-white); padding-top: 120px;">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-header" style="text-align: center;">
                <span class="section-tag" style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); color: var(--color-white);">Most Effective Treatment</span>
                <h1 class="section-title" style="color: var(--color-white); font-size: var(--font-size-4xl);">Mounjaro for Weight Loss</h1>
                <p class="section-subtitle" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;">A breakthrough dual-hormone weight loss treatment that targets both GLP-1 and GIP receptors for enhanced results</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- What is Mounjaro -->
    <section class="section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="content-wrapper" style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;">
                <h2 class="section-title">What is Mounjaro?</h2>
                <p>Mounjaro is a prescription-only injectable medication delivered via a self-administered pen designed for weekly use. The active ingredient is <strong>tirzepatide</strong>, classified as a GLP-1/GIP receptor agonist.</p>
                <p>This innovative treatment represents the latest advancement in weight loss medication, offering a dual-hormone approach that distinguishes it from traditional single-hormone treatments.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- How It Works -->
    <section class="section" style="background: var(--color-bg-alt);">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="content-wrapper" style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;">
                <h2 class="section-title">How Mounjaro Works</h2>
                <p>Mounjaro works by targeting two key digestive hormones—<strong>GLP-1</strong> and <strong>GIP</strong>—to curb your appetite and regulate your blood sugar levels. This dual-hormone approach is what makes Mounjaro particularly effective.</p>

                <div class="difference-grid" style="margin-top: var(--spacing-8);">
                    <div class="difference-item">
                        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="difference-icon">
                            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                            <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                        </svg>
                        <p><strong>Appetite Control:</strong> Reduces hunger and helps you feel fuller for longer</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="difference-item">
                        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="difference-icon">
                            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                            <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                        </svg>
                        <p><strong>Blood Sugar Regulation:</strong> Improves insulin sensitivity and glucose control</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="difference-item">
                        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="difference-icon">
                            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                            <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                        </svg>
                        <p><strong>Dual Hormone Action:</strong> Activates both GLP-1 and GIP receptors for enhanced effect</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Effectiveness -->
    <section class="section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="content-wrapper" style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;">
                <h2 class="section-title">Clinical Effectiveness</h2>
                <div style="background: var(--color-primary-50); padding: var(--spacing-8); border-radius: var(--radius-xl); border-left: 4px solid var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-6);">
                    <h3 style="color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-3);">Proven Results</h3>
                    <p style="font-size: var(--font-size-lg); margin: 0;"><strong>Clinical studies show Mounjaro can help reduce body weight by up to 22.5%</strong> when combined with diet and exercise, compared to just 3% with lifestyle changes alone.</p>
                </div>

                <h3>What to Expect</h3>
                <ul style="line-height: 1.8;">
                    <li><strong>First Month:</strong> Most people lose approximately 4% of body weight during the initial month on the starting dose of 2.5mg</li>
                    <li><strong>Progressive Results:</strong> Weight loss accelerates as doses increase over time</li>
                    <li><strong>Long-term Success:</strong> Maximum effectiveness achieved with consistent use and lifestyle modifications</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Who Can Use It -->
    <section class="section" style="background: var(--color-bg-alt);">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="content-wrapper" style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;">
                <h2 class="section-title">Who Can Use Mounjaro?</h2>
                <p><strong>Standard eligibility criteria include:</strong></p>
                <ul style="line-height: 1.8;">
                    <li>Individuals with a BMI of <strong>30 or higher</strong></li>
                    <li>OR BMI of <strong>27 or higher</strong> with weight-related health conditions</li>
                </ul>
                <p style="margin-top: var(--spacing-4); padding: var(--spacing-4); background: var(--color-white); border-radius: var(--radius-lg);"><em>Note: Private providers may prescribe at lower BMIs if clinical judgment supports the benefit-to-risk ratio for individual patients.</em></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Dosing -->
    <section class="section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="content-wrapper" style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;">
                <h2 class="section-title">Dosing Information</h2>
                <div class="difference-grid">
                    <div class="difference-item">
                        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="difference-icon">
                            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                            <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                        </svg>
                        <p><strong>Starting Dose:</strong> 2.5mg weekly injection</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="difference-item">
                        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="difference-icon">
                            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                            <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                        </svg>
                        <p><strong>Pen Capacity:</strong> Each pen contains four weekly doses</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="difference-item">
                        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="difference-icon">
                            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                            <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                        </svg>
                        <p><strong>Supply Cycle:</strong> New pens sent every four weeks</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="difference-item">
                        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="difference-icon">
                            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                            <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                        </svg>
                        <p><strong>Maintenance:</strong> Personalized dose determined by your clinical team</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div style="margin-top: var(--spacing-8); padding: var(--spacing-6); background: var(--color-bg-alt); border-radius: var(--radius-lg);">
                    <h3>Missed a Dose?</h3>
                    <p><strong>If 4 days or fewer have passed:</strong> Take the missed dose immediately</p>
                    <p><strong>If more than 4 days have passed:</strong> Skip that dose and resume your regular schedule</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Side Effects -->
    <section class="section" style="background: var(--color-bg-alt);">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="content-wrapper" style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;">
                <h2 class="section-title">Side Effects & Management</h2>

                <h3>Common Side Effects</h3>
                <p>Most people experience mild to moderate gastrointestinal effects, including:</p>
                <ul style="line-height: 1.8;">
                    <li>Nausea</li>
                    <li>Loose stools or constipation</li>
                    <li>Digestive discomfort</li>
                </ul>

                <p style="margin-top: var(--spacing-4);"><strong>Timeline:</strong> Side effects typically appear within days of your first injection or dose increases, with improvement within 2-4 weeks as your body adjusts.</p>

                <div style="margin-top: var(--spacing-8); background: var(--color-white); padding: var(--spacing-8); border-radius: var(--radius-xl);">
                    <h3 style="color: var(--color-primary);">Tips for Managing Side Effects</h3>
                    <div class="difference-grid">
                        <div class="difference-item">
                            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="difference-icon">
                                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                                <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                            </svg>
                            <p>Start with low doses and increase gradually</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="difference-item">
                            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="difference-icon">
                                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                                <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                            </svg>
                            <p>Maintain a simple diet during dose adjustments</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="difference-item">
                            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="difference-icon">
                                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                                <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                            </svg>
                            <p>Stay well hydrated throughout the day</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="difference-item">
                            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="difference-icon">
                                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                                <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                            </svg>
                            <p>Eat smaller portions more frequently</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="difference-item">
                            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="difference-icon">
                                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                                <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                            </svg>
                            <p>Avoid trigger foods (fatty, spicy, acidic items)</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="difference-item">
                            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="difference-icon">
                                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                                <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                            </svg>
                            <p>Limit alcohol and caffeine consumption</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="difference-item">
                            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="difference-icon">
                                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                                <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                            </svg>
                            <p>Keep a consistent injection schedule</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Mounjaro vs Wegovy -->
    <section class="section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="content-wrapper" style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;">
                <h2 class="section-title">Mounjaro vs Wegovy</h2>
                <p>Both medications are highly effective for weight loss, but there are some key differences:</p>

                <div class="comparison-table-wrapper" style="margin-top: var(--spacing-8);">
                    <div class="comparison-table">
                        <table>
                            <thead>
                                <tr>
                                    <th>Feature</th>
                                    <th>Mounjaro</th>
                                    <th>Wegovy</th>
                                </tr>
                            </thead>
                            <tbody>
                                <tr>
                                    <td><strong>Active Ingredient</strong></td>
                                    <td>Tirzepatide</td>
                                    <td>Semaglutide</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td><strong>Mechanism</strong></td>
                                    <td>Dual-hormone (GLP-1 + GIP)</td>
                                    <td>Single-hormone (GLP-1)</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td><strong>Maximum Weight Loss</strong></td>
                                    <td>Up to 22.5% at 15mg dose</td>
                                    <td>Up to 20.7% at maximum dose</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td><strong>Cardiac Benefits</strong></td>
                                    <td>Demonstrated in studies</td>
                                    <td>Licensed for cardiovascular protection</td>
                                </tr>
                            </tbody>
                        </table>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <p style="margin-top: var(--spacing-6);"><strong>Bottom line:</strong> Mounjaro typically delivers slightly greater weight loss due to its dual-hormone mechanism, while both medications have demonstrated cardiovascular benefits.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Special Considerations -->
    <section class="section" style="background: var(--color-bg-alt);">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="content-wrapper" style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;">
                <h2 class="section-title">Important Considerations</h2>

                <div style="background: var(--color-white); padding: var(--spacing-6); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-6);">
                    <h3 style="color: var(--color-primary);">Fertility & Pregnancy</h3>
                    <p>Mounjaro can improve fertility in women with PCOS through weight loss and improved insulin sensitivity. However:</p>
                    <ul style="line-height: 1.8;">
                        <li><strong>The medication is unsafe during pregnancy</strong></li>
                        <li>Must stop at least <strong>one month before</strong> attempting conception</li>
                        <li>Mounjaro reduces oral contraceptive effectiveness</li>
                        <li>Use non-oral contraception methods (IUD, implant) or barrier protection (condoms)</li>
                        <li>Additional contraception needed for <strong>4 weeks</strong> after starting treatment and each dose increase</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div style="background: var(--color-white); padding: var(--spacing-6); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-6);">
                    <h3 style="color: var(--color-primary);">Weight Maintenance</h3>
                    <p>Weight regain is common if you stop taking Mounjaro without maintaining the lifestyle changes built during treatment. Your appetite will gradually return to normal over several weeks as the medication clears your system.</p>
                    <p style="margin-top: var(--spacing-4);"><strong>Our support includes:</strong> Guidance on maintaining your weight loss through sustainable lifestyle habits even after treatment ends.</p>
                </div>

                <div style="background: var(--color-white); padding: var(--spacing-6); border-radius: var(--radius-lg);">
                    <h3 style="color: var(--color-primary);">How Quickly Does It Work?</h3>
                    <p>Mounjaro starts working within a few hours of your first injection, but it takes time to notice the effects:</p>
                    <ul style="line-height: 1.8;">
                        <li>Some people experience reduced appetite immediately</li>
                        <li>Others may require several weeks to notice changes</li>
                        <li>Effects become increasingly noticeable as doses escalate</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Safety -->
    <section class="section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="content-wrapper" style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;">
                <h2 class="section-title">Safety Profile</h2>
                <p>Mounjaro has demonstrated a strong safety profile through extensive clinical trials and regulatory review. It has been approved by the UK's MHRA (Medicines and Healthcare products Regulatory Agency) for both weight management and type 2 diabetes treatment.</p>

                <div style="background: var(--color-primary-50); padding: var(--spacing-8); border-radius: var(--radius-xl); border-left: 4px solid var(--color-primary); margin-top: var(--spacing-6);">
                    <h3 style="color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-3);">Our Commitment to Your Safety</h3>
                    <p style="margin: 0;">At Logan Health, our experienced pharmacists provide comprehensive monitoring and support throughout your treatment journey. We ensure Mounjaro is right for you and help you achieve the best possible results safely.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="section" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary-dark) 0%, var(--color-primary) 100%); color: var(--color-white);">
        <div class="container">
            <div style="text-align: center; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;">
                <h2 class="section-title" style="color: var(--color-white); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-4);">Ready to Start Your Journey with Mounjaro?</h2>
                <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); font-size: var(--font-size-lg); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-8);">Check your eligibility today and take the first step towards achieving your weight loss goals with expert support from Logan Health.</p>
                <div style="display: flex; gap: var(--spacing-4); justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;">
                    <a href="index.html#questionnaire" class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg">Check Eligibility</a>
                    <a href="index.html#contact" class="btn btn-outline btn-lg" style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); color: var(--color-white); border: 2px solid var(--color-white);">Contact Us</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</BaseLayout>
